# Bulak, Selenginsky District, Republic of Buryatia

}}
Bulak (; , Bulag) is a rural locality (an ulus) in Selenginsky District, Republic of Buryatia, Russia. The population was 21 as of 2010.
Geography
Bulak is located 7&nbsp;km northeast of Gusinoozyorsk (the district's administrative centre) by road. Gusinoozyorsk is the nearest rural locality.
